./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5495:      "note": "The dialogue established that method-type (self-confirming, self-canceling, self-dissolving) is upstream of whether remainder pressure arises. Remainder pressure is a dependent variable, not an independent hidden variable."
