./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5603:      "note": "The grain of the attentional training that performs negation shapes the residue that remainder pressure must account for; remainder pressure cannot be defined independently of the tradition-specific grain that produces it."
./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5609:      "note": "Once formalized as a typed functional variable rather than a phenomenological datum, remainder pressure may reduce to the domain-general problem of what happens when an operation is applied to the domain containing the operator. Specificity to contemplative practice is unresolved."
./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5621:      "note": "The proponent conceded that the authorization policy (ontologize, recurse, bracket, model, dissolve) is not applied sequentially after remainder pressure appears but co-arises with it. Practice instructions often encode the policy from the beginning."
./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5657:      "note": "Credit-distribution architecture determines whether a practice generates agent-driven negation and therefore whether subject-shaped residue arises. Practitioner-centered credit is most likely to produce remainder pressure; ground-centered and activity-centered credit may prevent it."
./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5663:      "note": "Once remainder pressure arises, the tradition's inference policy determines whether it is ontologized, recursively analyzed, bracketed, cognitively modeled, or dissolved by refusing the generating procedure."
./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5669:      "note": "Anti-search instructions (Huang Po), direct introduction (Dzogchen trekcho), and pre-completion declarations (Advaita praptasya praptih) block the negation procedure that would generate remainder pressure, rather than managing it after the fact."
./runs/20260529-063900-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-seed-joe-rogan-and-phy/prompt.md:5681:      "note": "The two-stage model (credit distribution upstream, remainder pressure downstream) is structurally stable only if the two variables are partially but not fully coupled. Full determination collapses the model upward; full independence collapses it downward."
