./runs/20260529-061525-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-use-this-exchange-betw/prompt.md:5407:      "note": "Once formalized as a typed functional variable rather than a phenomenological datum, remainder pressure may reduce to the domain-general problem of what happens when an operation is applied to the domain containing the operator. Specificity to contemplative practice is unresolved."
