./runs/20260529-061525-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-use-this-exchange-betw/prompt.md:5455:      "note": "Credit-distribution architecture determines whether a practice generates agent-driven negation and therefore whether subject-shaped residue arises. Practitioner-centered credit is most likely to produce remainder pressure; ground-centered and activity-centered credit may prevent it."
./runs/20260529-061525-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-use-this-exchange-betw/prompt.md:5461:      "note": "Once remainder pressure arises, the tradition's inference policy determines whether it is ontologized, recursively analyzed, bracketed, cognitively modeled, or dissolved by refusing the generating procedure."
./runs/20260529-061525-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-use-this-exchange-betw/prompt.md:5467:      "note": "Anti-search instructions (Huang Po), direct introduction (Dzogchen trekcho), and pre-completion declarations (Advaita praptasya praptih) block the negation procedure that would generate remainder pressure, rather than managing it after the fact."
./runs/20260529-061525-claude-probe-the-reality-of-time-use-this-exchange-betw/prompt.md:5479:      "note": "The two-stage model (credit distribution upstream, remainder pressure downstream) is structurally stable only if the two variables are partially but not fully coupled. Full determination collapses the model upward; full independence collapses it downward."
