./runs/20260530-094906-codex-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/codex-cli.stderr.log:52:The Free Energy Principle's predictive processing framework, when applied to contemplative self-negation, does not resolve the atman/anatta dispute but formally reproduces it at a higher level of abstraction. Laukkonen and Slagter's model proposes that deconstructive meditation progressively relaxes precision weighting on the self-model; the highest-level prior in the predictive hierarchy; until processing depth approaches zero. The critical question...
