reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:88:      "difference": "Dzogchen may not accept dissolution-gradient language, since the text emphasizes seeing the nature of mind rather than gradually dissolving a self-claiming layer.",
