reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:172:      "Tannisho, Taitetsu Unno translation, https://www.themathesontrust.org/papers/fareasternreligions/Tannisho-Unno.pdf",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:175:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The claimant-layer vocabulary is strongly shaped by Theravada categories and may distort Shinran, Dzogchen, Soto Zen, and traditions that reject agency accounting. The warning-cluster prediction also risks circular coding unless safeguards are coded from a separate corpus.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:176:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit found strong near-neighbors but did not fully close-read Steve Bein, Taitetsu Unno, Pargament, Lindbeck, Trungpa, VCE coding materials, Shinran's Kyogyoshinsho, Rennyo letters, or Tibetan manuals beyond the cited Longchen Rabjam text. It also did not check Pali, Japanese, or Tibetan terms directly.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:177:    "structural_observation": "SN 22.89 already separates a formal path achievement from a remaining gradient: the noble disciple has abandoned lower fetters and does not assume 'I am this,' yet residual 'I am' conceit, desire, and obsession remain until further contemplation uproots them. SN 45.8 gives a clear practitioner-agency grammar for right effort. Tannisho gives the opposite formal marker: entrusting, non-calculation, and Amida's working, while warning against claiming nembutsu as one's own practice. Cross-reading these texts supports the candidate's two-track architecture, but also shows that much of the architecture is already available in primary sources."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:186:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Khemaka, Shinran, Dzogchen instructions, Dogen, Pargament, Bein, Trungpa, VCE, and prior Lumenary ledgers, this idea says the comparative unit is a two-track transfer profile and predicts that safeguards cluster where formal agency grammar changes while partial dissolution leaves layer-specific reappropriation risks."
observations/codex/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes.md:32:This may psychologize traditions that do not frame their speech as repair. Pure Land nembutsu, Dzogchen pointing-out, sacramental speech, and communal prayer may work as entrustment, recognition, vow, or participation rather than as a remedy for a named modern wound. The model also risks making every teaching pass through modern therapeutic usefulness, which could flatten worship, metaphysics, ritual duty, and liberation claims. It weakens sharply if trained practitioners say the repair field adds no decision value beyond ordinary source criticism, teacher guidance, or spiritual-bypass screening.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:100:      "difference": "Dogen is not giving a general rule for cross-tradition borrowing by eclectic seekers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:103:      "source": "Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.thezensite.com/ZenTeachings/Dogen_Teachings/GenjoKoan_Aitken.htm"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:161:      "William James, The Varieties of Religious Experience, https://www.gutenberg.org/files/621/621-h/621-h.html, read against Ignatius of Loyola, Spiritual Exercises discernment rules, https://www.ignatianspirituality.com/making-good-decisions/discernment-of-spirits/rules-for-discernment/ and Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.thezensite.com/ZenTeachings/Dogen_Teachings/GenjoKoan_Aitken.htm"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:165:    "structural_observation": "Chandogya authorizes identity with subtle essence and Atman, while SN 22.59 refuses ownership and self-identification for all aggregates, including consciousness. That supports a strict doctrine gate. James already shifts religious judgment toward fruits, Ignatian discernment tests movements by effects, timing, desolation safeguards, and disclosure to a competent spiritual person, and Dogen resists certifying realization apart from enacted practice. These primary sources strongly anticipate contact, conduct, and correction as tests of lived use."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.json:177:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Smith, Freiberger, Panikkar, James, Ignatius, Dogen, Lindbeck, Asad, Wuthnow, Turkle, spiritual-bypassing literature, social prescribing, OCD reassurance research, and recent Lumenary contact-before-claim records, this candidate's only distinct claim is that a valid doctrine-protection test should not be handed to a lonely person as medicine unless it demonstrably increases safe contact, conduct, correction, and belonging."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "The idea assumes that private review is often the burden for depleted over-managers. If structure and review are the relieving container, then the model confuses over-management with the absence of safe holding. It also fails if Other Power, Dogen practice-realization, or community-held practice includes rigorous review, conduct correction, and formal repetition without harming agency."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:31:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Coders cleanly apply keep, release, and embody axes across Shinran, Dogen, Heart Sutra, MN 22, and apophatic sources without distortion, and the three fit variables do not predict held-out warnings or repairs."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:59:    "Dogen practice realization no gaining Bendowa Genjokoan",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:60:    "Shinran Other Power self power jinen honi hakarai",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:78:      "difference": "ACT does not use cross-tradition custody, vow, Other Power, or practice-realization grammar, and it does not frame the issue as an after-use review gate.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:135:      "Soto Zen teachers or scholars of practice-realization",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:136:      "Jodo Shinshu teachers or scholars of Other Power",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:147:      "Dogen practice-realization sources such as Bendowa or Genjokoan; Shinran and Tannisho Other Power sources, including https://shinranworks.com/commentaries/notes-on-once-calling-and-many-calling/ and Tannisho chapter 8 translations."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:150:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit still needs direct term-level work on Shinran's jinen honi and hakarai, Dogen's shusho-itto or practice-realization, apophatic unsaying, spiritual direction ethics, and ACT or CBT literature on self-monitoring. Source reliability is adequate for lowering novelty, not for promoting the model as a discovery.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-help-should-not-be-managed-fa2107c4aba3ff90.json:151:    "structural_observation": "MN 22 supports a tool-use and non-clinging pattern: a teaching can be used for crossing and then not possessed. The Heart Sutra strains a simple release rule because it denies attainment while preserving reliance on prajnaparamita. Dogen-style practice-realization strains it further because practice is not merely an instrument awaiting later review. Shinran Other Power also resists practitioner-owned handling because merit and final efficacy are not primarily self-managed. The candidate's strongest move is not method-release, which is old, but the fit gate that asks whether ownership, temporality, and available agency exist before prescribing review."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "No-threshold and inherited-practice cases, especially Dogen's practice-realization and lifelong ritual socialization without a remembered conversion event.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:5:    "confidence_effect": "This lowers confidence in the model as a general structure. It can survive only with mandatory values for no-threshold, inherited practice, practice-realization, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable. If those values become common, the model becomes a comparison discipline rather than a predictive theory.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:30:      "test_surface": "Split-source blind coding across Tannisho, Orange, SN 55.5, OCIA texts, Dogen, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra entry manual, and one Sufi or Christian contemplative initiation source.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:34:      "expected_observation": "Pairs with high preserve-bend-drop strain, for example grace versus vow or stream-entry versus practice-realization, produce lower inter-rater agreement and more practitioner objections than low-strain pairs.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:40:      "expected_observation": "Vow-held and grace-held grammars should produce warnings against self-reliance, calculation, or Pelagian self-initiation; investigation grammars should produce warnings around wrong view, poor attention, and bad association; practice-realization grammars should warn against gaining idea and waiting for a separate outcome.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:63:    "Tannisho Primal Vow entrusting no other good self effort",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:66:    "Dogen Bendowa practice enlightenment are one beginner practice original enlightenment",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:143:    "Add mandatory values for no-threshold, inherited practice, practice-realization, grace-held entry, vow-held entry, social-encounter entry, teacher-recognition entry, ritual-first entry, crisis entry, gradual socialization, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:157:      "Where would comparing your entry grammar to grace, vow, stream-entry, recognition, or practice-realization bend or drop meanings you regard as decisive?",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:165:      "Jodo Shinshu ministers familiar with shinjin and Other Power",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:167:      "Soto Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:168:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:175:      "Tannisho, BDK translation, especially chapters 1 to 3, https://bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:178:      "Dogen, Bendowa practice-realization passage, https://justdharma.org/practice-and-enlightenment-dogen-zenji/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.json:182:    "structural_observation": "Tannisho gives a vow-held entry grammar: the decisive threshold is firm entrusting in Amida's vow, with warnings against self-effort, esoteric seeking, and arbitrary interpretation. Orange gives a grace-first Christian entry grammar: even prayer, will, desire, faith, and assent are preceded by grace, so anti-Pelagian safeguards are structurally expected. SN 55.5 gives a different threshold grammar: association with admirable people, hearing true Dhamma, appropriate attention, and practice in accordance with Dhamma. It predicts safeguards around community, teaching, attention, and right practice, not grace or vow. Dogen's Bendowa strains the model because practice and realization are not two sequential states; the warning is against waiting for enlightenment outside practice. These texts support the idea that entry accounts predict warning profiles, but they also show high translation strain: grace, vow, stream-entry, and practice-realization are not interchangeable values of one neutral variable."
observations/codex/2026-05-26-practice-load-and-scaffold-fit.md:21:- Dialogue turn 1, Codex challenge introducing minimum participation scaffold and Shinran as a hard case.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-practice-load-and-scaffold-fit.md:24:- Primary and near-neighbor sources cited in the dialogue: SN 22.59, Chandogya Upanishad 6.8.7-6.16, Shinran's Tannisho and Kyogyoshinsho, Engler on being somebody before being nobody, Lindahl et al. on meditation-related challenges.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:27:- Tannisho sections I to X, https://nembutsu.cc/buddhism/the-tannisho/tannisho-sections-i-to-x/
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:30:Structural observation: The primary texts support distribution of direction, but they also reduce novelty. MN 10 does not present bare neutral attention, it gives frames, ardency, hindrance work, aggregate analysis, arising, and disappearance. Vivekachudamani directs the seeker from the start through discrimination, dispassion, teacher relation, and self-knowledge. Tannisho relocates decisive efficacy away from self-owned practice into entrusting and Other Power, even calling nembutsu non-practice and non-good from the practicer's side. Longchenpa's Trekcho instruction moves through preliminary deconstruction, teacher introduction, recognition of rigpa, and sustaining without effort or clinging. This close read supports the model's layer claim, but the structures are already visible in the sources themselves.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:34:Risk of overread: High. The model can become too absorbent if every difference is assigned to some layer after the fact. Tannisho and radical Other Power traditions can reject the analyst's practice-direction frame. Dogen-style practice-realization can collapse means and result. Bahiya-style immediacy strains any developmental layer sequence. Community, doctrine, teacher style, clinical risk, and social belonging may explain many cases without this model.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:47:- Tannisho non-practice non-good Other Power primary text
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:53:- Lutz, Jha, Dunne, and Saron, Investigating the Phenomenological Matrix of Mindfulness-Related Practices, https://www.johnddunne.net/uploads/9/8/5/6/9856107/lutzjhadunne___saron_investigating_the_phenomenological_matrix_of_mindfulness-related_practices_from_a_neurocognitive_perspective_american_psychologist_oct_2015_.pdf: overlap: Very close. The phenomenological matrix decomposes mindfulness practices into manipulable dimensions and explicitly includes posture, affective tone, axiological concerns, and practice instructions.; difference: It does not foreground teacher authorization, community interpretation, Other Power, or post-insight custody as comparative religion variables.; novelty impact: High reduction. Any empirical test must show predictive lift beyond this matrix.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:69:Candidate: Bahiya's immediate release, Tannisho's non-practice Other Power, and Dogen's practice-realization collapse the model's tendency to locate direction in analyzable layers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:71:Why it strains the model: Bahiya receives a brief instruction and is said to be released immediately, so textual coding cannot show whether direction came from prior training, readiness, teacher authority, or the instruction itself. Tannisho denies self-owned practice calculation and assigns decisive efficacy to Other Power, so calling nembutsu a directed practice can distort the source. Dogen-style practice-realization refuses a clean sequence of practice first and result later, so layer location may be an analyst imposition.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:73:Confidence effect: This lowers confidence from candidate discovery to extended. The model remains useful as a coding heuristic only if it includes analyst-frame-refused, no-threshold, practice-realization, radical Other Power, and undecidable values.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:77:- If: If direction layers have real explanatory force, split-source blind coders should infer warning and repair profiles from entry or instruction texts before reading manuals or interviews. Then: Layer scores should predict held-out warnings and repairs above baselines using tradition name, technique family, teacher style, social ecology, Pargament agency style, Lutz matrix dimensions, and VCE factors. Weakens if: Low inter-rater reliability, no predictive lift, or equally strong predictions from simpler baselines would weaken the model. Test surface: Six-case corpus: MN 10, Vivekachudamani, Tannisho, Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual, and The Cloud of Unknowing.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:88:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:106:Answers that support contribution: Practitioners provide concrete cases where a layer-coded mismatch predicts a repair that a generic technique, tradition, or clinical-risk model misses, for example when a noting-trained student applies deconstructive effort inside direct recognition, or when a Pure Land convert treats nembutsu as self-owned achievement despite instruction to entrust.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:131:- Add mandatory values for no-threshold, inherited practice, practice-realization, radical Other Power, direct recognition, teacher-held, vow-held, grace-held, community-held, no-practice-frame, no-direction-frame, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.md:136:- Use Bahiya, Tannisho, Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, direct introduction, and successful dual practice as anomaly classes rather than confirming examples.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:12:Before asking what a practice does with authority over its result, ask whether it claims to produce a separable result at all. Custody, release, and correction vocabulary applies only to instrumental practices. Dogen's practice-realization and Shinran's Other Power dissolve the tool frame because sitting or entrusting is not owned as a means to a later product.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:18:- Dogen's practice-realization makes sitting not a bridge to later enlightenment but the expression of realization itself.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:19:- Shinran's Other Power denies practicer calculation and owned efficacy.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:27:- Dogen shusho itto and Shinran jinen honi, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf and https://shinranworks.com/hymns-in-japanese/hymns-of-the-dharma-ages/on-jinen-honi/
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:29:Structural observation: MN 22 is explicitly instrumental: effort with the raft gets one across, then the raft should not be carried. Dogen's shusho itto demolishes the cause-effect separation between practice and realization, while Shinran's jinen honi removes calculation by the practicer and locates efficacy in Other Power. The contrast supports a scope distinction, but not a discovery: the instrumental versus non-instrumental contrast is already structurally visible in the primary texts.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:31:Secondary literature gap: The audit did not read Eihei Shingi, full Bendowa or Genjokoan in Japanese, Shinran's Japanese around jinen and hakarai, Tannisho anti-license passages in Japanese, ritual theory in depth, Aristotle praxis and poiesis sources, or empirical studies of autotelic practice and perfectionism. These are necessary before raising novelty.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:33:Risk of overread: High. Non-instrumental self-description does not mean absence of discipline, correction, warnings, institutional form, or effects. Dogen still requires continuous practice, and Shinran still has nembutsu, entrusting, and cautions. The model may confuse no owned result with no practical structure.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:37:- Dogen shusho itto practice realization one cause effect practice realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:38:- Shinran jinen honi no calculation Other Power practicer
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:39:- Tannisho nembutsu not practice not good act Other Power self power
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:49:- Internal Lumenary audit, When There Is Nothing To Keep Or Release, reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json: overlap: Extremely close. The prior audit already says keep, release, embody assumes practitioner ownership and a discrete after, and that Shinran and Dogen break those assumptions.; difference: This candidate uses the broader word instrumentality and asks whether the practice claims to produce a separable result.; novelty impact: Major internal downgrade. The scope-gate framing is useful but not a new discovery.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:51:- Dogen shusho itto, Soto Zen key term, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf: overlap: Very close. The source states that shusho itto demolishes the generally accepted cause-effect relation between practice and realization.; difference: The candidate turns this into a scope rule for Lumenary's custody apparatus.; novelty impact: Downgrades the Dogen example to known Soto doctrine.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:52:- Shinran, On Jinen Honi, https://shinranworks.com/hymns-in-japanese/hymns-of-the-dharma-ages/on-jinen-honi/: overlap: Very close. Shinran explicitly rejects practicer calculation and describes Other Power as no working, which undermines self-owned method efficacy.; difference: The candidate uses Shinran as a non-tool boundary case rather than as Pure Land doctrine alone.; novelty impact: Downgrades the non-ownership claim to known primary-text structure.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:55:- Pargament et al., religious problem-solving styles, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for agency distribution between individual and divine action, especially deferring and collaborative styles.; difference: Pargament studies coping and control attribution, not whether a practice produces a separable result.; novelty impact: For Shinran-style agency relocation, novelty is low unless the separable-result gate predicts warnings beyond agency-style variables.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:59:Unlike Dogen's practice-realization, Shinran's Other Power, autotelic activity theory, non-instrumental ritual theory, MacIntyre's internal goods, and prior Lumenary non-ownership audits, this idea's possible contribution is a practical scope gate for comparative coding: ask first whether a practice claims to produce a separable result before applying custody, release, or correction vocabulary.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:65:Why it strains the model: If Eihei Shingi, Soto training, Shinran's cautions against licensed evil, nembutsu practice, and community transmission all function as retained disciplines with real effects, then non-instrumentality is not outside the custody apparatus. It is a different custody location: form-held, vow-held, teacher-held, conduct-held, or community-held.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:71:- If: The separable-result question is a real scope gate. Then: Texts and manuals coded as non-instrumental from doctrinal passages will show less result-custody language and more conduct, form, vow, teacher, or community correction language in held-out sources. Weakens if: Self-described non-instrumental traditions contain result-custody language as centrally as instrumental traditions, or coders cannot distinguish result refusal from result relocation. Test surface: Split-source coding of Dogen, Shinran, MN 22, koan curricula, Advaita inquiry, apophatic Christian sources, Sufi fana and baqa, and ritual manuals.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:78:- Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:93:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners and scholars say this is already standard as practice-realization, Other Power, autotelic ritual, internal goods, non-attachment, grace, or non-gaining mind, and that the scope gate adds no predictive guidance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:113:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.34. The instrumental versus non-instrumental distinction is old and appears directly in Dogen, Shinran, ritual theory, autotelic activity theory, and prior Lumenary non-ownership audits. The useful extension is narrower: using separable-result as a pre-coding scope gate for Lumenary's custody and release apparatus. Human-condition fit is strong for functioning perfectionists, founders, students, creators, and professionals who convert every activity into proof of worth. It is not for under-motivation, responsibility avoidance, severe depression, dissociation, mania, psychosis, addiction withdrawal, acute crisis, coercive workloads, or people who need concrete completed outcomes restored before resultless practice is safe.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-practice-is-a-tool-6243c8e923d5f36f.md:120:- Read non-instrumental ritual theory, autotelic flow literature, MacIntyre on practices, Dogen's Eihei Shingi, Bendowa and Genjokoan, Shinran and Tannisho in stronger translations before public use.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:27:      "expected_observation": "Jodo Shinshu warns against self-power calculation, Orange-Augustinian grace traditions warn against pride and presumption, Dzogchen warns against premature recognition and fabrication, and social-encounter models warn against isolation from good friends or teachers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:35:      "test_surface": "Comparative coding of primary texts and doctrinal manuals across Confucian, Theravada, Pure Land, Christian, Dzogchen, Yogacara, and Zen sources.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:62:    "Dzogchen pointing out instruction recognition rigpa awareness recognizes itself",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:73:      "difference": "Augustine is a single-tradition theological solution, not a comparative typology across Buddhist, Pure Land, Christian, and Dzogchen cases.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:124:    "Close-read Tannisho chapter 1, Orange canons 3-7, SN 55.5, Mencius 2A6, Longchenpa Trekcho, and a Yogacara transformation-of-basis source before publication.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:130:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.78 to about 0.62. The cross-tradition variable and downstream prediction are promising, but the first-break circularity is strongly anticipated by Meno's paradox, Augustine and Orange on the beginning of faith, James and Rambo on conversion, Rahner, Kotva, Yogacara, Dzogchen pointing-out, and transformative learning. Do not call it a discovery until the typology outperforms these prior frames in manual coding and practitioner tests.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:145:      "Dzogchen and Mahamudra teachers",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:157:    "risk_of_overread": "Moderate to high. The model may project a philosophical bootstrapping problem onto practitioners who begin through family, ritual, obedience, attraction, crisis, community, or habit without experiencing a paradox. It may also collapse distinct cases: Shinran's Other Power and Orange's prevenient grace are structurally close, while Dzogchen self-disclosure and Platonic recollection may be closer than the typology admits.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:158:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The strongest prior art includes Plato's Meno on inquiry into what one does not know, Augustine and Orange on initium fidei, William James on volitional and self-surrender conversion, Rambo's conversion stages, Rahner's supernatural existential, Simone Kotva on effort and grace, Yogacara asraya-paravrtti, Dzogchen pointing-out literature, and transformative learning theory. The audit did not find the exact four-value cross-tradition typology with downstream predictions, but most structural ingredients are already named in adjacent literatures.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-first-break-problem-a1081d3f97040016.json:171:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Meno, Augustine, Orange, James, Rambo, Rahner, Kotva, Yogacara, and Dzogchen sources, this idea claims that the first-break mechanism is a cross-tradition variable that predicts later effort theory, verification, safeguards, and failure modes. That comparative-predictive use is the main contribution, not the circularity itself."
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:23:- Primary-text comparison: Dogen's Bendowa refuses a separation between cultivation and realization while still recommending direct practice, https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf. Huangbo's On the Transmission of Mind refuses seeking as a way to grasp mind, consulted via Blofeld PDF record, https://merton.bellarmine.edu/s/merton/media/51897, and Chan transmission analysis, https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/12/4/279. Shinran's Tannisho denies self-powered practice while preserving teacher, vow, and correction against divergence, https://jodoshinshu.faith/tannisho-a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:24:- Thinking method source: Dogen's practice-realization was used as a lens to stop assuming before, after, method, and result. Critique of that lens: it can dissolve real sequence too quickly, so it was checked against Shinran's warnings about calculation and Huangbo's sharper refusal of seeking.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:31:Huangbo may weaken the model from inside it. His search-refusal can be read as refusing not only private ownership but also every mediating support the analyst wants to name. Calling his discourse a support may domesticate a teaching meant to cut support-seeking itself. Dogen also strains the model because practice-realization may not relocate support at all; practice may simply be the expression, not a holder of continuity. A further weakness is circularity: coders may find support wherever a tradition has teachers, texts, or communities, which would make the model descriptive rather than predictive. The claim should be weakened if no-distance practitioners flourish without identifiable correction supports, or if their failures do not cluster around privatization, passivity, or performance.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:87:Survives the anomaly that Dogen, Huangbo, and Shinran each refuse a simple method-then-result timeline, yet each still preserves some form of practice, discourse, vow, teacher, or warning against distortion.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:161:- Next action: Search extended cognition, ritual studies, Pure Land studies, Dogen studies, Chan studies, Dzogchen studies, and mindfulness critique for this exact scope condition.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:171:- Next action: Code Bendowa, Uji, Huangbo, Tannisho, selected Dzogchen manuals, and practitioner reports for ownership refusal, correction holder, and named failure mode.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:196:- If this model is right, then Dogen-style, Huangbo-style, Shin-style, and Dzogchen-style texts should refuse private ownership while still protecting some concrete source of correction. If they deny both ownership and corrigible support, the model is weakened.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-even-no-path-needs-care.md:200:- Protocol improvement: Dogen's lens should remain a warning against false sequence, not a universal solvent. Pair it with a method that preserves concrete responsibility, such as early Buddhist not-mine analysis or Shinran's warning against self-power calculation.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-residual-burden-of-proof-after-negation-735d12569e257535.json:76:    "Add separate rubric values: direct recognition, scriptural assertion, inference, pragmatic bracketing, recursive testing, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-residual-burden-of-proof-after-negation-735d12569e257535.json:84:    "answers_that_support_contribution": "Experts say the field distinguishes direct recognition, scriptural assertion, inference, pragmatic bracketing, and recursive testing in ways existing self/no-self comparisons blur.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:26:- Dogen Bendowa practice-realization, read through Carl Bielefeldt, Dogen's Manuals of Zen Meditation, https://www.ucpress.edu/books/dogens-manuals-of-zen-meditation/pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-borrowed-words-need-shared-life-f614444030865666.md:28:Structural observation: Chandogya 6.8.7 authorizes identity through the repeated Self teaching, while SN 22.59 dismantles ownership of the aggregates, including consciousness, through impermanence and lack of control. The same surface function, loosening ordinary identity, is carried by incompatible verification rules. Dogen adds pressure against treating a sentence apart from enacted practice. This supports a carrier-context warning, but it does not prove that contact-first routing is original.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings.md:29:The candidate may still compress a messy causal ecology into one elegant frame. Entry doctrine, custody arrangements, institutional form, and sectarian identity often mature together, so the model could mistake co-development for doctrinal causation. Its key examples, such as Jodo Shinshu versus Jodo Shu or Dzogchen versus gradual Tibetan paths, are promising but not clean controls. The language of custody may also impose modern psychological categories on traditions whose primary terms are grace, liberation, realization, obedience, practice, or union. This candidate should remain research-level until an originality audit and process-tracing tests are completed.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings.md:57:- Use matched comparisons, especially Jodo Shinshu versus Jodo Shu, Dzogchen versus gradual Tibetan sutra-path practice, and explicit grace traditions versus neighboring cooperation traditions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.md:26:- William James, The Varieties of Religious Experience, https://www.gutenberg.org/files/621/621-h/621-h.html, read against Ignatius of Loyola, Spiritual Exercises discernment rules, https://www.ignatianspirituality.com/making-good-decisions/discernment-of-spirits/rules-for-discernment/ and Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.thezensite.com/ZenTeachings/Dogen_Teachings/GenjoKoan_Aitken.htm
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.md:28:Structural observation: Chandogya authorizes identity with subtle essence and Atman, while SN 22.59 refuses ownership and self-identification for all aggregates, including consciousness. That supports a strict doctrine gate. James already shifts religious judgment toward fruits, Ignatian discernment tests movements by effects, timing, desolation safeguards, and disclosure to a competent spiritual person, and Dogen resists certifying realization apart from enacted practice. These primary sources strongly anticipate contact, conduct, and correction as tests of lived use.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.md:51:- Dogen, Genjokoan, https://www.thezensite.com/ZenTeachings/Dogen_Teachings/GenjoKoan_Aitken.htm: overlap: Close on enacted verification and resistance to treating realization as a possession certified before practice.; difference: Dogen is not giving a general rule for cross-tradition borrowing by eclectic seekers.; novelty impact: Supports the analogy but lowers novelty of action-before-identity logic.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-a-test-is-not-a-home-84a684343a09d2ca.md:58:Unlike Smith, Freiberger, Panikkar, James, Ignatius, Dogen, Lindbeck, Asad, Wuthnow, Turkle, spiritual-bypassing literature, social prescribing, OCD reassurance research, and recent Lumenary contact-before-claim records, this candidate's only distinct claim is that a valid doctrine-protection test should not be handed to a lonely person as medicine unless it demonstrably increases safe contact, conduct, correction, and belonging.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-grid-stays-backstage.md:61:- Ask Soto, Shinran, Zen, Advaita, and clinical mindfulness teachers whether keep-release-embody is a faithful translation, useful pastoral adaptation, or doctrinal distortion.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Dogen's Bendowa practice-realization, especially the claim that training and enlightenment are not two, https://www.abuddhistlibrary.com/Buddhism/C%20-%20Zen/Ancestors/Dogen/Bendowa/Bendowa.htm",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:5:    "confidence_effect": "Lowers confidence in the model as a universal explanatory structure. It remains useful as a comparative heuristic, but the anomaly blocks promotion above novel_synthesis until Dogen, Pure Land, Dzogchen, and Christian grace cases are coded without distortion.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "If practice and realization are one, then load-transfer language can create the separation Dogen rejects. Zazen is not simply practitioner agency carrying a burden, nor divine or vow relocation. It is enactment of realization. The ledger can handle this only by adding values such as no-transfer, no-boundary, and analyst-frame-refused. Those values may save accuracy but weaken explanatory compression."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:29:      "expected_observation": "Independent coders should infer later manual warnings and safeguards from early claims about self, liberation, and final transformation at above-chance rates. For example, Other Power texts should warn against calculation, practice-realization texts should warn against treating practice as a means to a later goal, and deconstructive paths should warn against reification and dissociation.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:31:      "test_surface": "Blind coding trial across SN 45.8, Tannisho, Bendowa, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra manual, one Christian grace manual, and one Sufi fana or baqa source.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:37:      "test_surface": "Structured interviews with dual-trained practitioners in Theravada and Pure Land, Advaita and bhakti, Zen and Dzogchen or Mahamudra, plus teacher reports of student switching failures.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:47:      "expected_observation": "Jodo Shinshu, Dzogchen, Mahamudra, and Christian grace teachers should accept some functional preconditions while objecting to capacity ownership language. Their corrections should cluster around vow-held, teacher-held, grace-held, recognition-event, and analyst-frame-refused values.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:49:      "test_surface": "Practitioner-scholar interviews and manual coding of Shinran, pointing-out instructions, and grace texts.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:67:    "Tannisho chapter 8 nembutsu not practice good act self power calculation other power translation Unno PDF",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:68:    "Dogen Bendowa practice realization enlightenment are one text translation",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:79:      "difference": "Engler is mainly psychodynamic and Buddhist practice-facing. He does not supply a comparative vector ledger across grace, vow, nondual recognition, self-power, and practice-realization traditions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:121:      "difference": "Tannisho is one primary path grammar, not a comparative model. It may be better treated as an anomaly than as support.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:123:      "overlap": "Very close for load relocation and forbidden self-claiming. Tannisho explicitly denies that nembutsu is the practitioner's self-powered practice or good act.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:124:      "source": "Shinran and Tannisho on Other Power, https://www.themathesontrust.org/papers/fareasternreligions/Tannisho-Unno.pdf and practitioner summary, https://tricycle.org/article/self-power-and-other-power/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:130:    "Add explicit values for practitioner-owned, teacher-held, vow-held, grace-held, community-held, text-held, practice-realization, recognition-event, no-transfer, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:131:    "Close-read Shinran's Tannisho and letters, SN 45.8, Bendowa or Genjokoan, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual, one Christian grace text, and one Sufi fana or baqa source before public use.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:137:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.70 to about 0.61. The scalar-to-vector move is useful, but its parts are strongly anticipated by Pargament's agency styles, Engler's developmental prerequisites, Dahl and Lutz's meditation mechanism taxonomies, VCE adverse-effect variables, Hadot's spiritual exercises, Ferrer's participatory pluralism, Katz and Sharf's contextualism, Buddhist upaya, and Shinran's Other Power. The remaining contribution is a promising operational synthesis with testable predictions, not a discovered law of spiritual paths.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:144:      "Does directionality predict actual sequencing, warnings, and repair instructions for students, or is it obvious under older terms such as upaya, grace, self-power, Other Power, or ego development?",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:145:      "When practitioners move between effort, surrender, vow, recognition, and practice-realization paths, do they need a reorientation practice, or only more maturity and guidance?",
