reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:162:      "Tannisho, sections VII to IX, translated by Taitetsu Unno, https://www.themathesontrust.org/papers/fareasternreligions/Tannisho-Unno.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:164:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The ledger may turn tradition-specific soteriology into analyst-owned cells. Pure Land entrusting, Dogen practice-realization, and Dzogchen recognition may not be practitioner capacities at all, even when they have observable preconditions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:165:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit searched Pargament, Engler, Hadot, Ferrer, Katz, Sharf, Dahl, Lutz, Davidson, Lindahl, Britton, upaya literature, Tannisho, Bendowa, and SN 45.8. It did not close-read Shinran's letters, Kyogyoshinsho, Longchenpa, Wangchuk Dorje, Christian grace manuals, Sufi fana and baqa texts, or original Pali and Japanese terms. That gap blocks any candidate-discovery claim.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:166:    "structural_observation": "SN 45.8 reads like a high-agency ledger: right view knows suffering and cessation, right resolve is directed toward renunciation and harmlessness, right effort generates desire and persistence, right mindfulness maintains ardent attention, and right concentration stabilizes the path. Tannisho VIII reverses the ownership grammar: nembutsu is not the practitioner's practice or good act because it is Other Power and free of self-power. Tannisho IX treats lack of joy not as simple incapacity but as blind passion already anticipated by the vow. The pair supports the vector insight because similar path functions are assigned different direction and locus. It also threatens the model because calling entrusting a capacity may already distort Shinran's grammar."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:175:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Pargament, Engler, Dahl, Hadot, Ferrer, Katz, Sharf, upaya theory, and Shinran, this idea claims that path requirements can be coded as a reusable vector ledger where each functional role has magnitude, direction, locus, stage, safeguards, and failure mode, and that whole-path soteriology may generate the direction of each role. Its possible contribution is predictive rubric design, not the discovery that traditions differ in agency, capacity, or context."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-residual-burden-of-proof-after-negation-735d12569e257535.md:82:Answers that support contribution: Experts say the field distinguishes direct recognition, scriptural assertion, inference, pragmatic bracketing, and recursive testing in ways existing self/no-self comparisons blur.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-residual-burden-of-proof-after-negation-735d12569e257535.md:105:- Add separate rubric values: direct recognition, scriptural assertion, inference, pragmatic bracketing, recursive testing, and undecidable.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Direct-recognition and practice-realization lineages, such as Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out, Dogen practice-realization, and Pure Land Other Power.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:28:      "expected_observation": "Usable inter-rater agreement on roles such as assertion, instruction, warning, defense, report, repair, praise, direct recognition, and analyst-frame-refused across Brihadaranyaka 3.7.23, SN 22.59, SN 22.95, Udana 1.10, Heart Sutra, Dogen, and one pointing-out manual.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:36:      "test_surface": "Practitioner interviews with Advaita, Theravada, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Zen, spiritual direction, and contemplative-science practitioners.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:61:    "Dzogchen pointing out instruction words perform recognition not description",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:104:    "Build a sentence-role codebook with values for assertion, instruction, warning, defense, report, repair, praise, direct recognition, mechanism, identity verdict, inseparable performative, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:106:    "Add anomaly cases before public use: Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out, Dogen practice-realization, Pure Land Other Power, and competent direct-recognition settings.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:125:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:126:      "Zen teachers familiar with Dogen practice-realization",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:136:    "risk_of_overread": "High. Role coding can become a way to soften or evade direct doctrinal claims. A passage can be both assertion and instruction, or both warning and ontology. English translations may hide genre and grammar. Direct-recognition, practice-realization, and Other Power cases may refuse clean separation among word, act, gift, recognition, and result. The human-condition use is plausible only for stable overinterpreters, not for acute panic, psychosis, mania, dissociation, trauma amnesia, active addiction withdrawal, medical blackouts, OCD or scrupulosity loops, unsafe authority settings, or people already under competent guidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.json:137:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Before publication, search Austin and Searle on speech acts, SEP Religious Language, Lindbeck on doctrine as grammar, Asad on discursive tradition, Sharf on rhetoric of meditative experience, Katz and Proudfoot on mediated religious experience, Taves on experience attribution, Freiberger on comparative method, Buddhist upaya and raft-simile literature, Ignatian discernment, Dogen practice-realization, Pure Land Other Power, and Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals. Also compare internal records: Stratified Post-Negation Authorization, Stop Making Silence Judge You, No Silence Proves Itself, You Cannot Prove the One Who Is Asking, and When Tools Become Judges.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:12:    "Shinran's Other Power refuses practitioner ownership, calculation, and self-generated entrusting.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:13:    "Dogen's practice-realization refuses the separation between method, verification, and later custody.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:25:  "exact_claim": "The keep, release, embody model silently assumes that the practitioner provisionally owns the method and that there is an after in which custody of the result can be decided. Radical Other Power and practice-realization break those assumptions: in Shinran's jinen honi the practitioner never owns the method, trust, or result, while in Dogen's shusho-itto there is no discrete after outside practice. Therefore the custody model is bounded, and for depleted over-managing people the prompt to decide what to keep, release, or embody can become one more burden.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:32:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Coders cannot separate refusal from relocation, or retain, release, embody categories work equally well across Shinran, Dogen, Advaita, Theravada, Rinzai, apophatic Christian, and Sufi sources."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:41:      "expected_observation": "The same practitioner is more likely to reject keep, release, embody language when speaking from Jodo Shinshu or Soto practice-realization than when speaking from Advaita inquiry, vipassana, therapy, or productivity training.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:50:    "Shinran jinen honi no calculation Other Power natural working of the primal vow",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:51:    "Tannisho nembutsu not practice not good act practicer Other Power self power",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:52:    "Dogen Bendowa practice realization one shusho itto verification outside practice",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:53:    "Dogen practice and realization are one scholarship",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:63:      "overlap": "Extremely close. Both argue that release teaching applies to active-voice result-ownership, while Other Power, practice-realization, and no-attainment sources strain or refuse the release frame.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:67:      "difference": "The candidate uses Shinran as a scope condition for a comparative after-use model and as a modern caution for over-management.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:69:      "overlap": "Very close for the non-ownership claim: natural working and Other Power oppose practicer calculation and self-generated control.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:70:      "source": "Shinran, On Jinen-Honi, https://shinranworks.com/letters/lamp-for-the-latter-ages/on-jinen-honi-1258/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:76:      "source": "Tannisho, A Record in Lament of Divergences, https://shinranworks.com/related-works-by-other-authors/a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:91:      "difference": "The candidate connects that clinical risk to theological non-ownership and practice-realization boundary cases.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:101:    "Close-read Shinran's Japanese terms around jinen honi and hakarai, Dogen on shusho-itto and non-gaining, and practitioner manuals where concrete guidance appears.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:104:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.28. The non-ownership and no-after structures are well established in Shinran and Dogen, and the core Lumenary comparison is already present in the recent audit of You cannot release what you never held. The modern caution overlaps with known rumination, perfectionism, and burnout risks. Human-condition fit is strong for depleted over-managers, caregivers, founders, professionals, students, and serious practitioners who turn even rest into performance. It is not for people who need planning, accountability, medication, therapy, social support, or material workload reduction, nor for acute crisis, addiction withdrawal, severe depression, dissociation, psychosis, mania, or responsibility avoidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:107:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners say the distinction is already standard as Other Power, practice-realization, grace, surrender, non-calculation, or non-gaining mind, and that the no-audit prompt is simply rest from rumination or basic clinical caution.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:117:      "Soto Zen teachers and Dogen scholars",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:127:      "Shinran, On Jinen-Honi and Tannisho, https://shinranworks.com/letters/lamp-for-the-latter-ages/on-jinen-honi-1258/ and https://shinranworks.com/related-works-by-other-authors/a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:128:      "Dogen, Bendowa and shusho-itto practice-realization sources, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:130:    "risk_of_overread": "Moderate to high. The claim may exaggerate refusal into absence. Other Power and practice-realization may not abolish all custody questions; they may relocate custody to vow, teacher, text, sangha, conduct, or practice itself. The human-condition claim may also overgeneralize depletion, since some burned-out people need structure and accountability rather than non-audit.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:131:    "secondary_literature_gap": "This audit did not read Japanese sources, Dogen commentarial scholarship, Jodo Shinshu scholarship, grace-effort theology, Pargament's full agency-style work, or ethnographic practitioner accounts. It also did not verify whether other traditions with inherited practice, ritual-first formation, or apophatic unsaying similarly refuse the ownership-and-after assumptions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:132:    "structural_observation": "Shinran relocates efficacy to Other Power and warns against calculation, so the practitioner is not the owner who later decides how to carry the method. Dogen's practice-realization collapses the gap between practice and verification, so a later custody decision is not the native shape of the path. These are strong boundary cases against a universal after-use grid, but they do not eliminate all guidance: Shin still has nembutsu, warnings, and entrusting language, and Soto still has zazen, discipline, teacher correction, and conduct."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.json:144:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Shinran's Other Power, Dogen's practice-realization, Pargament's agency styles, burnout rumination literature, and prior Lumenary release and custody models, this idea's possible contribution is an explicit scope test: before applying keep, release, or embody guidance, first ask whether the tradition grants provisional practitioner ownership and a discrete after, and whether the person has enough agency to benefit from a custody prompt."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:19:- Zhuangzi, Dzogchen, and Sufi fana are classified as self-dissolving because the practitioner or frame of method becomes irrelevant.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:30:Secondary literature gap: I did not find an exact three-type typology of contemplative methods as confirming, canceling, and dissolving at completion. But the self-canceling portion has very strong prior art in Nagarjuna, Wittgenstein ladder readings, Buddhist raft discussions, and Sells on apophatic unsaying. The dissolving portion is also standard in fana, zuowang, and Dzogchen descriptions. The new part is the comparative axis and its predicted consequences, not the individual patterns.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:32:Risk of overread: High. The model imposes a modern reflexive category, method's relation to itself, on traditions that may speak instead of upaya, realization, grace, direct recognition, non-grasping, or annihilation of ego. It also risks treating stage-specific pedagogies as stable types.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:68:- If: Method-type should predict verification architecture better than tradition membership. Then: Eckhart and Nagarjuna should share more indirect, anti-possessive verification patterns with each other than Eckhart shares with more kataphatic Christian mystics. Advaita witness practice should use more direct recognition language than Madhyamaka critique. Weakens if: Christian sources cluster together by tradition more strongly than by method-type, or all traditions use the same teacher, lineage, and conduct criteria regardless of method relation. Test surface: Coded comparison of practice manuals, teacher testing language, and post-realization instructions across at least six traditions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:69:- If: Dual-trained practitioners should report different relations to their own insight when switching method-types. Then: After Advaita inquiry, practitioners describe recognition as stable witness or Self. After Heart Sutra or Madhyamaka practice, they resist treating any insight as an attained object. After Dzogchen or fana language, they emphasize effortless presence or transformed embodiment over method success. Weakens if: Practitioners report no stable difference, or differences track teacher personality and institutional context more than method-type. Test surface: Structured interviews with practitioners trained in more than one contemplative lineage.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:70:- If: Hybrid traditions should show explicit boundary management between method stages. Then: Texts should mark when to use, trust, undermine, release, or embody a method. Examples would include raft language, preliminary versus main practice, koan curriculum before and after kensho, or thorn-removing-thorn metaphors. Weakens if: No boundary markers appear, or methods freely confirm, cancel, and dissolve without any pedagogical distinction. Test surface: Historical and textual analysis of Zen, Dzogchen, Advaita, Madhyamaka, Sufi, and Christian apophatic training sequences.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:78:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:113:- Search further for upaya, raft, ladder, thorn-removes-thorn, Gelassenheit, fana and baqa, rang grol, and practice-realization as exact structural near-neighbors.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology.md:28:- Shinran, Tannisho
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Pure Land nembutsu and Dogen practice-realization.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "These may not be best understood as tools that repair a named modern wound. Nembutsu can function as entrusting gratitude under Other Power, and Dogen can refuse a separable tool-result model. Forcing them through a repair-survival gate may distort the native practice before it protects the borrower."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:120:    "Add anomaly cases before public use: Pure Land nembutsu, Dogen practice-realization, Dzogchen pointing-out, sacramental speech, communal prayer, and non-instrumental ritual."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.json:150:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The model risks forcing traditions into modern therapeutic repair language. Pure Land nembutsu, Dzogchen pointing-out, sacramental speech, Dogen practice-realization, communal prayer, and ritual duty may function through vow, grace, recognition, participation, or formation rather than a named wound. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: stable unsupported seekers facing meaning loss, digital comparison, loneliness, and achievement-contingent certainty. It is not fit for acute crisis, dissociation, psychosis, mania, severe depression, OCD or scrupulosity loops, addiction withdrawal, unsafe authority, or medical blackout concerns.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:26:- Tannisho and Rennyo Ofumi, BDK English Tripitaka, https://www.bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:28:- Dogen shusho itto source from Soto Zen, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:30:Structural observation: Orange is a near-exact high-severity case: prayer, will, desire, assent, and the beginning of faith are attributed to grace, not unaided nature. Tannisho supplies a vow-held analogue, where entrusting to Amida's Primal Vow displaces self-power and reshapes warning language. SN 22.59 does not fit the same entry grammar, because it negates ownership of aggregates and moves through disenchantment and release without clearly requiring an external break mechanism. Dogen is the strongest anomaly: practice and realization are treated as one, and beginner practice is already implicated in realization, so entry and fruition cannot be cleanly sequenced as threshold and later attainment.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:32:Secondary literature gap: The audit checked accessible primary translations, local prior Lumenary audits, and open sources on conversion, liminality, doctrine-as-grammar, religious coping, legitimate peripheral participation, contemplative adverse effects, grace, Other Power, and practice-realization. It did not fully review Rambo's full monograph, Lindbeck's full book, Japanese, Pali, Sanskrit, Tibetan, Latin, or Chinese originals, Shinran scholarship, Dogen scholarship, Sufi bayah and fana sources, Dzogchen pointing-out manuals, or practitioner interviews.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:34:Risk of overread: High. The model can become circular if incapacity, threshold, break mechanism, residue policy, and predicted safeguards are extracted from the same passage. It also risks forcing traditions with inherited practice, continuous formation, no-threshold participation, or practice-realization into an analyst's entry grid.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:47:- "Tannisho" Other Power self power Primal Vow chapter 11
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:48:- "Dogen" Bendowa practice realization shusho itto
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:61:- Shinran and Tannisho Other Power sources, https://www.bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf: overlap: Near exact for vow-held entry, blocked self-credit, warning against self-power, and transformation disclosed through entrusting.; difference: Tannisho is a primary case rather than a generalized comparative instrument.; novelty impact: Very high reduction for Other Power examples and for denial of self-generated threshold entry.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:62:- Dogen practice-realization and shusho itto, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf: overlap: Strong anomaly and near-neighbor for no-threshold entry: practice and realization are one, and beginner practice is already original realization.; difference: The candidate can code this only by adding no-threshold, no-break, practice-realization, and analyst-frame-refused values.; novelty impact: High anomaly pressure. Without these values the model overreaches.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:68:Unlike Rambo, Lofland-Stark, Van Gennep, Turner, Lindbeck, Pargament, Lave and Wenger, Orange, Shinran, Dogen, VCE, Meno-style inquiry paradoxes, and prior Lumenary entry-residue records, this idea says entry should be coded through four interacting fields, incapacity, minimum participation, break mechanism, and residue policy, and that first-break type becomes irreducible only where a tradition denies that ordinary self-generated threshold entry can found the path.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:72:Candidate: Inherited religious formation and Dogen-style practice-realization.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:74:Why it strains the model: In inherited formation, there may be no discrete threshold act, no single first break, and no separate residue policy available to the beginner. In Dogen-style practice-realization, beginning and realization are not cleanly separated, so the entry grammar may be the same as the fruition grammar. These cases force the model to include no-threshold, no-break, continuous-authorization, practice-realization, and analyst-frame-refused values.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:80:- If: High-severity traditions that deny self-generated threshold entry should show distinctive warnings against self-credit or self-powered attainment. Then: Entry texts coded as grace-held, vow-held, or teacher-recognition entry should predict held-out warning texts targeting pride, self-effort absolutism, unauthorized claim-making, despair, passivity, or premature certainty. Weakens if: If held-out manuals from these traditions warn no more against self-credit than matched traditions with ordinary participation thresholds, the first-break variable loses predictive force. Test surface: Split-source coding across Orange and Augustinian grace texts, Tannisho and Shinran letters, Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, and matched Theravada or Confucian cultivation texts.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:82:- If: Residue policy should interact with entry grammar rather than merely duplicate it. Then: Two traditions with similar entry thresholds but different residue policies should show different verification rules and different forbidden claimant warnings. Weakens if: If residue policy adds no predictive gain beyond entry mechanism, support locus, social ecology, and tradition identity, the compound model should collapse into simpler entry or agency models. Test surface: Compare Theravada no-self analysis, Advaita self-inquiry, Pure Land Other Power, Soto practice-realization, and Dzogchen recognition using inter-rater coding and held-out warning manuals.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:83:- If: First-break should be non-universal. Then: Gradual cultivation, inherited practice, legitimate peripheral participation, and practice-realization cases should be codeable without a first-break field, or should receive a no-break or analyst-frame-refused value. Weakens if: If all cases require first-break accounting, the conditional claim is false. If none do after controls, the first-break field is unnecessary. Test surface: Initial six-case trial: Theravada sangha entry, Confucian cultivation, Jodo Shinshu, Augustinian grace, Zen great doubt, and Dzogchen pointing-out.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:92:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:99:- Is this four-field grammar more than familiar conversion theory, grace versus works, self-power versus Other Power, upaya, doctrine-as-grammar, and ordinary lineage pedagogy?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:105:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners say this is already obvious as conversion stages, initiation, grace, Other Power, self-power, upaya, doctrine-as-grammar, socialization, or apprenticeship. They cannot identify cases where the four fields predict warnings or repairs better than tradition identity, teacher experience, institutional context, or clinical risk.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:125:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.54. The four-field compression is useful, but most components have strong near-neighbors in prior Lumenary audits, conversion theory, rites-of-passage theory, doctrine-as-grammar, religious problem-solving styles, legitimate peripheral participation, grace theology, Pure Land Other Power, Dogen practice-realization, VCE factor coding, and Meno-style inquiry paradoxes. The remaining contribution is a conditional first-break rule plus a split-source predictive test, not a discovery-level doctrine candidate.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:133:- Add mandatory values for no-threshold, no-break, inherited practice, gradual socialization, ritual-first entry, vow-held entry, grace-held entry, teacher-recognition, practice-realization, continuous authorization, radical Other Power, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.md:135:- Test six initial cases: Theravada sangha entry, Confucian cultivation, Jodo Shinshu, Augustinian grace, Zen great doubt, and Dzogchen pointing-out.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "No-threshold practice-realization, inherited religion, and successful dual-practice cases.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:5:    "confidence_effect": "This lowers confidence in the model as a general theory. It can survive only as a coding heuristic with mandatory values for no-threshold, inherited-practice, practice-realization, simultaneous-custody, no-custody-frame, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "The candidate assumes a distinguishable beginning where some holder takes custody before the practitioner can authorize the path. Dogen-style practice-realization weakens the before-after sequence because practice and realization are not two separate states. Inherited religion can make beginning indistinguishable from ordinary socialization. Successful dual practice can show multiple support systems coexisting without a single contested custody arrangement."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:31:      "test_surface": "Split-source blind coding across Orange, Tannisho or Ofumi, Benedictine novitiate texts, OCIA, SN 55.5 and related Theravada manuals, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra entry source, and one Sufi or Islamic initiation source.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:63:    "Tannisho Other Power self-power entrusting Primal Vow",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:77:      "overlap": "Very close. That audit already codes entry grammar, predicts safeguards and beginner warnings, requires split-source testing, and compares grace, vow, stream-entry, and practice-realization under translation strain.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:93:      "difference": "It studies micro-sociological ritual learning, not custody assignment across grace, vow, rule, teacher, ritual, and practice-realization grammars.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:119:      "overlap": "Near exact for vow-held beginning, Other Power, blocked self-credit, critique of calculation, and gratitude rather than self-powered production after entrusting.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:120:      "source": "Shinran and Rennyo, Tannisho and Ofumi, https://bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:140:    "Add mandatory values for inherited practice, no-threshold, practice-realization, gradual socialization, ritual-held custody, community-held custody, teacher-held custody, vow-held custody, grace-held custody, rule-held custody, text-held custody, self-authorized entry, simultaneous custody, no-custody-frame, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:141:    "Run matched comparisons where social ecology can be partially controlled, especially Jodo Shinshu versus Jodo Shu, Augustinian grace traditions versus synergist neighbors, Benedictine novitiate versus less formal lay formation, OCIA versus inherited Catholic formation, and Dzogchen pointing-out versus gradual Tibetan path training.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:143:    "Treat Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, successful dual practice, and traditions that reject agency accounting as anomaly classes rather than confirming examples.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:147:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.76 to about 0.43. The candidate is generative, but most of its structure is already present in local Lumenary records, especially Entry-State Ledger, Threshold Grammar Under Translation Strain, Compound Entry Grammar, Layered Authorization of Beginning, and Operational Remainder Ecology. External near-neighbors further reduce the claim: Rambo covers conversion process, Lave and Wenger cover pre-mastery participation, Kupari and Utriainen apply that to religious newcomers, Lindbeck covers doctrine as grammar, Pargament covers agency distribution, Orange and Shinran give near-exact prescriptive beginning cases, Benedict and OCIA give institutional formation cases. The remaining contribution is a sharper label for prescriptive versus retrospective custody, not a discovery-level idea.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:150:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners and scholars say the frame is ordinary grace theology, Other Power, catechumenate, monastic formation, refuge, initiation, lineage pedagogy, doctrine-as-grammar, religious coping, conversion studies, or legitimate peripheral participation. They cannot identify repairs predicted by custody grammar beyond institution, teacher experience, community ecology, temperament, or clinical risk.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:166:      "Soto Zen teachers familiar with practice-realization",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:167:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:175:      "Shinran and Rennyo, Tannisho and Ofumi, BDK English Tripitaka, https://bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:179:    "risk_of_overread": "Very high. Custody is a modern analyst term that can flatten grace, vow, obedience, refuge, rule, catechesis, initiation, community socialization, and practice-realization into one psychological metaphor. The model also risks circularity if the same passage is used to infer custody grammar and then to confirm predicted warnings or repairs.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:180:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Search and close-reading covered accessible primary texts, local prior Lumenary records, conversion theory, legitimate peripheral participation, doctrine-as-grammar, catechumenate sources, religious coping, ritual learning, and contemplative adverse-experience methodology. It did not fully review Rambo's full monograph, Lindbeck's The Nature of Doctrine, Talal Asad in full, Van Gennep and Turner in full, Japanese Pure Land scholarship, Dogen scholarship, Tibetan pointing-out manuals, Islamic bayah and Sufi tarbiya sources, Sanskrit guru-disciple materials, original-language sources, or practitioner interviews.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:181:    "structural_observation": "Orange is the strongest prescriptive incapacity case: faith's beginning, desire, assent, prayer, and right choice are assigned to grace rather than unaided natural power. Tannisho and Ofumi give a vow-held analogue: entrusting is given by Amida's working, nenbutsu after settled faith is gratitude rather than self-powered production, and the warning profile targets calculation and self-power. Benedict gives institutional and apprenticeship custody: the novice is delayed, tested, placed under a senior, repeatedly exposed to the Rule, and only then incorporated. SN 55.5 is a partial anomaly: it names association with people of integrity, hearing true Dhamma, appropriate attention, and practice in accordance with Dhamma. That is distributed support, but not necessarily a doctrine forbidding self-generated beginning. The close-read result is that the candidate's structure exists in several sources, but its categories are analyst abstractions over older grace, vow, rule, apprenticeship, and stream-entry grammars."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.json:190:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike prior Lumenary entry ledgers, Rambo conversion theory, legitimate peripheral participation, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar, Pargament's agency styles, Orange, Shinran, Benedict, and OCIA, this candidate's only distinct claim is that beginnings should be coded as custody of unstable attention, trust, agency, and interpretation, and that entry doctrine should be classified as either retrospective narration or prescriptive control. That difference is useful but thin, because prior Lumenary records and older sources already contain most of the structure."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Valid solitude or direct recognition with stable ethical fruit, plus cases where external correction is abusive, shaming, or dependency-producing.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.json:40:      "expected_observation": "Advaita, Dzogchen, Zen, and apophatic sources that speak of direct recognition still point to conduct, teacher verification, scripture, vows, lineage, compassion, or ordinary functioning as later constraints.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.json:41:      "if_model_is_right": "Traditions that claim direct recognition still retain some corrective channel.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-silence-needs-correction-06ae06e9a81492e8.json:136:      "Advaita and Dzogchen teachers who teach direct recognition",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Bahiya's immediate release, Tannisho's non-practice Other Power, and Dogen's practice-realization collapse the model's tendency to locate direction in analyzable layers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:5:    "confidence_effect": "This lowers confidence from candidate discovery to extended. The model remains useful as a coding heuristic only if it includes analyst-frame-refused, no-threshold, practice-realization, radical Other Power, and undecidable values.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "Bahiya receives a brief instruction and is said to be released immediately, so textual coding cannot show whether direction came from prior training, readiness, teacher authority, or the instruction itself. Tannisho denies self-owned practice calculation and assigns decisive efficacy to Other Power, so calling nembutsu a directed practice can distort the source. Dogen-style practice-realization refuses a clean sequence of practice first and result later, so layer location may be an analyst imposition."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:30:      "test_surface": "Six-case corpus: MN 10, Vivekachudamani, Tannisho, Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual, and The Cloud of Unknowing.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:64:    "Tannisho non-practice non-good Other Power primary text"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:80:      "difference": "It does not foreground teacher authorization, community interpretation, Other Power, or post-insight custody as comparative religion variables.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:138:    "Add mandatory values for no-threshold, inherited practice, practice-realization, radical Other Power, direct recognition, teacher-held, vow-held, grace-held, community-held, no-practice-frame, no-direction-frame, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:143:    "Use Bahiya, Tannisho, Dogen practice-realization, inherited religion, direct introduction, and successful dual practice as anomaly classes rather than confirming examples.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:150:    "answers_that_support_contribution": "Practitioners provide concrete cases where a layer-coded mismatch predicts a repair that a generic technique, tradition, or clinical-risk model misses, for example when a noting-trained student applies deconstructive effort inside direct recognition, or when a Pure Land convert treats nembutsu as self-owned achievement despite instruction to entrust.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:162:      "Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:176:      "Tannisho sections I to X, https://nembutsu.cc/buddhism/the-tannisho/tannisho-sections-i-to-x/",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:179:    "risk_of_overread": "High. The model can become too absorbent if every difference is assigned to some layer after the fact. Tannisho and radical Other Power traditions can reject the analyst's practice-direction frame. Dogen-style practice-realization can collapse means and result. Bahiya-style immediacy strains any developmental layer sequence. Community, doctrine, teacher style, clinical risk, and social belonging may explain many cases without this model.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-direction-of-practice-e59e1c607fa2dc18.json:181:    "structural_observation": "The primary texts support distribution of direction, but they also reduce novelty. MN 10 does not present bare neutral attention, it gives frames, ardency, hindrance work, aggregate analysis, arising, and disappearance. Vivekachudamani directs the seeker from the start through discrimination, dispassion, teacher relation, and self-knowledge. Tannisho relocates decisive efficacy away from self-owned practice into entrusting and Other Power, even calling nembutsu non-practice and non-good from the practicer's side. Longchenpa's Trekcho instruction moves through preliminary deconstruction, teacher introduction, recognition of rigpa, and sustaining without effort or clinging. This close read supports the model's layer claim, but the structures are already visible in the sources themselves."
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-question-must-fit-the-wound.md:21:- Thinking method source: Huangbo, On the Transmission of Mind, used as a search-refusal lens. It made me ask whether the question itself was the grip. Critique of the lens: it can make every analytic question look like grasping, so it was checked against early Buddhist investigation and modern safety screening. https://gutenberg.org/ebooks/25236
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-question-must-fit-the-wound.md:23:- Primary text comparison: SN 22.59 authorizes a disciplined search through body, feeling, perception, formations, and consciousness; Dogen's Bendowa strains a before-and-after reading by treating practice and verification as inseparable; Shinran's reply to Senshin refuses calculation by the practicer; Huangbo warns against seeking Mind as an object. The comparison shows that the same question can be native medicine, imported distortion, or unsafe burden. https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/SN/SN22_59.html; https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf; https://shinranworks.com/letters/a-collection-of-letters-zensho-text/what-we-call-other-power/
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-question-must-fit-the-wound.md:29:This may be a safety wrapper around ordinary good judgment, not a new doctrine-building insight. It may also become one more burden for the over-managing cohort: before practicing, they must now audit the question, the wound, and the support. Rinzai koan and huatou practice are major anomalies, because an impossible or destabilizing question can be the medicine rather than the mistake. Dogen, Huangbo, Shinran, and Dzogchen cases may also be too diverse for one gate: they may refuse self-owned attainment while still preserving strong practice, teacher, vow, or conduct demands. The claim weakens if blind coders cannot identify the permitted question before reading later warnings, if practitioner failures track sleep loss, trauma, isolation, or teacher abuse better than question mismatch, or if ordinary rest and honest conversation work as well as this practice.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-question-must-fit-the-wound.md:160:- Next action: Search Zen great doubt studies, Pure Land scholarship, Dogen studies, Dzogchen instruction, spiritual direction ethics, and clinical spiritual-bypassing literature for the exact three-gate formulation.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-question-must-fit-the-wound.md:167:- Prediction: If the model is right, blind coders given instruction passages from SN 22.59, MN 22, Bendowa, Shinran, Huangbo, Rinzai koan sources, and Dzogchen instructions should identify permitted question, refused question, correction holder, and likely non-fit cohort above chance before seeing later warnings or outcomes. If they cannot, the model is weakened.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-the-question-must-fit-the-wound.md:208:- Close-read SN 22.59, MN 22, Bendowa, Shinran's letters, Huangbo, a Rinzai koan source, and one Dzogchen pointing-out source with a split-source codebook: permitted question, refused question, holder of correction, warning, repair, and human non-fit case.
