reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.md:95:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with direct introduction
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.md:102:- Where would comparing your entry grammar to grace, vow, stream-entry, recognition, or practice-realization bend or drop meanings you regard as decisive?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.md:134:- Add mandatory values for no-threshold, inherited practice, practice-realization, grace-held entry, vow-held entry, social-encounter entry, teacher-recognition entry, ritual-first entry, crisis entry, gradual socialization, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.
