reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:59:- Tannisho and Jodo Shinshu Other Power sources, https://bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf: overlap: Very close for vow-held custody plus entrusting as the human-side interface. Self-power calculation already functions as a named failure mode.; difference: The candidate generalizes the structure across traditions and asks whether entrusting-like surfaces differ from custody itself.; novelty impact: Large reduction for Pure Land examples. Novelty can only be comparative and predictive.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:61:- Dzogchen and Mahamudra pointing-out instruction literature and practitioner-facing sources, for example https://vajrayana.tergar.org/course/dzogchen-three-words-immersion: overlap: Close for teacher-mediated recognition, readiness, recognition failure, and post-recognition stabilization.; difference: The candidate compares recognition with entrusting, investigation, loving attention, non-fabrication, and embodied presence under one rubric.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction. The recognition case is not new, but cross-case separability testing may add value.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:65:Unlike Pargament's agency styles, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar, Asad's discursive tradition, VCE adverse-effects research, upaya capacity pedagogy, Pure Land Other Power, Christian attention and grace theology, pointing-out instruction, and prior Lumenary ledgers, this idea says that the assigned holder of transformation and the practitioner's required mode of availability should be coded separately, then tested to see whether the second variable predicts warnings, sequencing, teacher repairs, and verification beyond the first.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:69:Candidate: Dogen-style practice-realization, inherited communal practice, and radical Other Power cases where the analyst cannot cleanly separate custody, entry, and receiving surface.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:71:Why it strains the model: If practice and realization are nondual, there may be no discrete landing event and no separate receiving surface. If a person is gradually formed by inherited communal participation before explicit assent, the receiving surface may be socialized rather than locally chosen. If radical Other Power refuses any self-power residue, calling entrusting a human surface may distort the doctrine by reintroducing the agency it rejects.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:73:Confidence effect: Lowers confidence from candidate discovery to extended. The model needs analyst-frame-refused, no-threshold, inherited-practice, practice-realization, radical-other-power, and undecidable values before use.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:77:- If: Receiving surface is not reducible to custody assignment. Then: Within the same custody class, such as vow-held, grace-held, or teacher-held paths, different receiving surfaces will correlate with different warning profiles and repair instructions. Entrusting failures should be repaired differently from recognition failures, investigation failures, or loving-attention failures. Weakens if: If custody assignment alone predicts warnings, sequencing, verification, and repairs as well as the two-variable model, receiving surface is redundant. Test surface: Split-source blind coding of Pure Land, Christian contemplation, Dzogchen or Mahamudra, Theravada insight, and Advaita manuals, followed by practitioner interviews.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:85:- Jodo Shinshu ministers familiar with shinjin, Other Power, and non-calculation
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:87:- Dzogchen or Mahamudra teachers familiar with pointing-out, recognition, guru relation, and stabilization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:90:- Soto Zen teachers familiar with shikantaza and practice-realization
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:97:- Does this model predict any sequencing or safeguard you would not already derive from upaya, grace theology, Other Power teaching, spiritual direction, teacher experience, or adverse-effects research?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:120:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.77 to about 0.55. The idea is useful and testable, but most components are strongly anticipated by prior Lumenary ledgers, Pargament's religious coping styles, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar, Asad's discursive tradition, VCE and teacher-factor research, upaya capacity pedagogy, Pure Land Other Power, Christian attention and grace theology, and pointing-out models. The remaining contribution is the explicit separability test between custody assignment and receiving surface.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:127:- Add mandatory custody values: vow-held, grace-held, teacher-held, causal-process-held, community-held, ritual-held, hidden-Self-held, practitioner-held, practice-realization, inherited-practice, no-threshold, radical-other-power, no-custody-frame, and undecidable.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.md:130:- Compare predictive value against Pargament agency styles, Lindbeck grammar, Asad discursive tradition, VCE variables, upaya capacity pedagogy, grace theology, Other Power scholarship, pointing-out instruction literature, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
